            "author_association": "NONE",
            "body": "Sorry ... you are right!\nIt was [ChatGPT](https://chatgpt.com/share/69ddfebf-6688-832c-8221-bf5adb8b0e0b) that has claimed that Vim does have 'args' and I did not check it.\n\nIf neither Vim nor NeoVim have such a sessionoption in any of their docs its not a bug but rather an Enhancement which would make the session management of NeoVim a bit \"more logical\". At least to what I consider as more logical... ;-)\n\nIf you think that my Issue would be a valid and useful Enhancement, you may leave my Issue as an Enhancement. If you consider my arguments about the behavior is not relevant enough, you may close it.\n\nThanks a lot for your support!",
