            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "We are tracking an epic to reimplement sessions in https://github.com/neovim/neovim/issues/34204 , and that will lead to a much more flexible feature.\n\nHowever I don't think we would add a new 'sessionoptions' flag for this. Instead a `SessionWritePre` event would allow you to do `:%argdel` easily.\n\nThere was a stalled attempt to add `SessionWritePre` here:\n\n- https://github.com/neovim/neovim/pull/23000\n\nLet's repurpose this issue to track that.",
